{
  "stem": "17543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 170.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just give me some light food-- you know, sort of boiled egg and just light food, you know-- semolina pudding, and you know, just light food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wouldn't think of giving me any heavy food, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was quite a while in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was quite a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was, again, some people who was coming and organizing what happened with people after leave the hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was put into a home where it was all young people who had no parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not necessarily because of the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It can be because the mother left them for some reason.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did you feel at this time, being on your own like that?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I tell you that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said I never pray again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never put my feet into a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I never tell anybody I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I have no-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't believe in a God who allowed to that happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's still with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeah, I can't help it, but that's the way I am.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is-- it's terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the people talking about their religious-- people taking about their Messiah-- Messiah, but if he hadn't came when was needed, don't bother to come now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's too late.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, in this home, we had clean everything and food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all were sent to learn something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was learned in a factory for two years as a learner for-- it is was a menswear factory, but what was it?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like conveyor belt the clothes was going, so I was just on one or another section.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't know what was the date when I became-- not a learner, because I kept doing the same thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
